	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So Jeroen was right and I was very wrong...CopyNES is compatible with a standard socket. It's just a REALLY tight fit. 
<br />
<br />What ended up working for me was pushing the socket onto the CopyNES board, then fitting that onto the NES board, then soldering it down.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
